---
export const prerender = true;
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About PlainVitamins"
  description="Learn about PlainVitamins' data source, methodology, and mission to make dietary supplement information freely accessible."
  breadcrumbs={[{ name: 'Home', href: '/' }, { name: 'About' }]}
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">About PlainVitamins</h1>
    <div class="prose max-w-none space-y-6 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
      <p class="text-lg">PlainVitamins makes dietary supplement information freely accessible. Browse supplements, ingredients, and brands using official government data from the NIH Dietary Supplement Label Database (DSLD).</p>

      <div class="bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-950/30 border border-amber-200 dark:border-amber-800 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-sm text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-200"><strong>Important:</strong> PlainVitamins does not recommend supplements or provide medical advice. The information shown is factual data from the NIH DSLD and should not replace professional medical judgment. Always consult a healthcare provider before starting any supplement.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)]">Data Source</h2>
      <p>All data comes from the <strong>National Institutes of Health (NIH) Dietary Supplement Label Database (DSLD)</strong>. The DSLD contains label information from dietary supplement products marketed in the United States, including ingredient lists, serving sizes, and manufacturer details.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)]">What Data We Show</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
        <li><strong>Supplement products</strong> with full ingredient breakdowns</li>
        <li><strong>Active ingredients</strong> and their amounts per serving</li>
        <li><strong>Brand information</strong> and product catalogs</li>
        <li><strong>Rankings</strong> and comparisons across categories</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)]">Important Notes</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
        <li>Dietary supplements are not evaluated by the FDA for efficacy</li>
        <li>Label data may not reflect current formulations</li>
        <li>Always verify supplement details with the manufacturer</li>
        <li>PlainVitamins is not affiliated with NIH or any government agency</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)]">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions or feedback? Reach us at hello@plainvitamins.com.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
